# 🧠 Sentiment Analyzer

A simple and powerful **Sentiment Analysis Tool** built with Python and TextBlob.  
It can analyze emotions from text or entire files and classify them as 😊 Positive, 😐 Neutral, or 😞 Negative.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Analyze any sentence or paragraph.
- Upload and analyze text files.
- Web interface built with **Flask**.
- CLI (Command Line) support.
- Emoji-based sentiment results.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Python 🐍
- Flask 🌐
- TextBlob 💬
- HTML / CSS 🎨

---

